# Trivy ignored vulnerabilities
# =============================
# Entries in this file are accepted risks with documented justification.
# Each entry MUST include:
#   - CVE-ID or ID
#   - Expiry date (YYYY-MM-DD) after which the entry must be reviewed
#   - Justification
#
# Format: <CVE-ID> [<expiry>] [<justification>]
#
# Example:
# CVE-2024-99999 2025-06-01 Temporarily ignored until upstream patch lands
